title: Visits to Iowa Cities by Political Party, Iowa, 2008
name: Visits to Iowa Cities by Political Party, Iowa, 2008
description: This dataset shows the number of visits by presidential candidates to each city in Iowa leading up to the 2008 Iowa caucus. Visits are shown as totals and by party. this data was accessed January 2nd 2008. Source: Des Moines RegisterURL: http://data.desmoinesregister.com/caucus/map1.php
